law.history: Repealed 2002 Ky. Acts ch. 351, sec. 18, effective July 15, 2002. -- Amended 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 476, sec. 22, effective July 14, 2000. -- Created 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 496, sec. 8, effective April 10, 1998.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Approval to reenter state for insurer that ceased doing business after July 15, 1995, and before April 10, 1998.
